git add src/install.rs && git commit -m "$(cat <<'EOF'
fix: use correct CC hooks format (matcher + hooks array, not command)

The Claude Code settings.json hook format requires:
  { "matcher": "", "hooks": [{ "type": "command", "command": "..." }] }
not:
  { "matcher": "", "command": "..." }

Also handles detection of both formats in already-installed check.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
EOF
)" && git push 2>&1
